---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="From the CEO's Desk"
  description="A message from Gurpreet Shahpuri, Founder and Educator at Mantra Academy, with 15+ years of teaching experience."
  path="/ceo-message"
>
  <section class="section ceo">
    <div class="container ceo__inner">
      <div class="card ceo__card">
        <div class="ceo__header">
          <img
            class="ceo__photo"
            src="/images/gurpreet-shahpuri.jpg"
            alt="Gurpreet Shahpuri, Founder and Educator at Mantra Academy"
            width="200"
            height="200"
          />
          <div>
            <p class="eyebrow">From the CEO's Desk</p>
            <h1>Gurpreet Shahpuri</h1>
            <p class="ceo__role">Founder &amp; Educator at Mantra Academy<br />15+ years of teaching experience</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="ceo__message">
          <p>
            When I started teaching, I noticed the same pattern again and
            again: students weren't struggling because they were incapable —
            they were struggling because they'd been rushed past concepts
            they never properly understood. By the time a topic became
            "old," the gaps were still there, just buried under new chapters.
          </p>
          <p>
            Mantra Academy exists to fix that. We slow down where it counts,
            make sure a concept actually lands before moving forward, and
            build confidence the only way it's really built — through
            genuine understanding, not shortcuts.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every student who walks in unsure of themselves in Maths or
            Science is, in my experience, just a student who hasn't yet had
            someone explain it properly and patiently. That's what we aim
            to be for every family that joins us.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .ceo__inner { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .ceo__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .ceo__photo {
    width: 140px;
    height: 140px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex: none;
    border: 4px solid var(--color-mustard);
  }
  .ceo__role { color: var(--color-mustard); font-weight: 700; margin: 0; }
  .ceo__message p { font-size: var(--step-0); }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .ceo__header { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
  }
</style>